      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在元宵节央视大裤衩配楼着火的时候，我正在湘江边上欣赏另一出烟花表演。<br>
州官放火，百姓点灯，真是其乐融融一派和谐啊。</p>
<p>江边的人群实在拥挤，沿江风光带的栏杆边上围了至少三层人，还不断有人下到江岸抢占有利位置。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278581568/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3412/3278581568_e10ec5db7e.jpg" alt="看烟花的人群 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278577102/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3521/3278577102_a2170a927c.jpg" alt="看烟花的人群 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>于是烟花燃放完毕后，场面就变得恐怖了，还好没有出现踩踏的事故。<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278649118/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3533/3278649118_64ef0bffaf.jpg" alt="看烟花的人群 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>虽然到达的时间比较晚，却抢占了有利的地形拍照，只可惜满意的照片不多：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278532884/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3470/3278532884_374052f4d5.jpg" alt="湘江上的元宵烟花 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278597018/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3387/3278597018_8bddd0d312.jpg" alt="湘江上的元宵烟花 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>人群散去之后，就只有激光射灯在孤独的摇摆：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278669478/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3313/3278669478_bd03a0570f.jpg" alt="IMG_6440 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a><br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3278684378/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3472/3278684378_c6a0acccd2.jpg" alt="IMG_6445 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>太平街的戏台非常难得的有表演，应该是《白蛇传》吧：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3277911051/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3527/3277911051_dc536b4251.jpg" alt="白蛇传 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p>元宵节前一天在太平街口看到的正准备挂起来的灯笼：<br>
<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/3277653611/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3453/3277653611_70d0321408.jpg" alt="灯笼 (by&lt;br&gt;
calon)"  />
</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/calon/sets/72157613783847173">更多照片</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
